description: Kona Truck of Boca Raton will make your next shaved ice experience a fun one. The only shaved ice with a built-in Flavorwave system where kids of all ages can create and discover a variety of tropical flavors. The perfect partner to book for your next special event or fundraiser, Kona Truck will be proud to give back to its community. Where fun hits the street!
name: Kona Ice of Boca Raton
